SINGULAR for Debian
===================
by Mathias Schulze <mschulze@mathematik.uni-kl.de>

To build Singular packages for Debian based systems run (with 4.0.0 replaced by the respective Singular version):
$ mv singular-4.0.0.tar.gz singular_4.0.0.orig.tar.gz
$ tar xzvf singular_4.0.0.orig.tar.gz
$ cd singular-4.0.0
$ debuild -us -uc 

To install the newly created packages run (as superuser, replacing amd64 by your architecture and 4.0.0 by the respective Singular version):
$ cd ..
$ dpkg -i singular_4.0.0-1_amd64.deb singular-bin_4.0.0-1_amd64.deb singular-common_4.0.0-1_all.deb

